<h2 id="νΈλ―Έλ¶„">νΈλ―Έλ¶„</h2>

<p>μ ) \(f\left(x,\ y\right)\ =\ 2x\ +\ 3xy\ +\ y3\) μ— λ€ν•΄,</p>

<ol>
  <li>
    <p>λ³€μ xμ— λ€ν•μ—¬ νΈλ―Έλ¶„ <br />
\(\frac{\partial f\left(x,y\right)}{\partial x}\ =\ \frac{\partial \left(2x\ +\ 3xy\ +{y}^3\right)}{\partial x}\ =\ 2\ +\ 3y\)</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>λ³€μ yμ— λ€ν•μ—¬ νΈλ―Έλ¶„ <br />
